<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>계정 이용 정지 안내</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c8d8f0 0%, #dce8f8 40%, #b8cce8 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed; min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; position: relative;
        }
        body::before {
            content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.12) 1px,transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.12) 1px,transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px; opacity: .35; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
        }

        /* 왼쪽 */
        .hero-panel {
            width: 380px; flex-shrink: 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px); background: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
            border-right: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.8);
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
            padding: 52px 44px; position: sticky; top: 0; height: 100vh; z-index: 1;
        }
        .logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; color: #1e3a8a; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .logo .hl { color: #2563eb; }
        .hero-icon {
            width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 22px;
            background: rgba(239,68,68,.1); border: 1.5px solid rgba(239,68,68,.2);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 22px;
        }
        .hero-title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: #172554; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .hero-desc { font-size: 14px; color: #4a6fa5; line-height: 1.8; }

        /* 오른쪽 */
        .content-panel { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 52px; z-index: 1; }
        .content-inner { width: 100%; max-width: 480px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }

        /* 카드 */
        .glass-card {
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px); background: rgba(255,255,255,.58);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.85); border-radius: 24px; padding: 28px 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(37,99,235,.1), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.9);
            position: relative;
        }
        .glass-card::before { content:''; position:absolute; left:10%; right:10%; top:0; height:1px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.9),transparent); }
        .card-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #ef4444; letter-spacing: .5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }

        .info-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,.06); }
        .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
        .info-label { font-weight: 700; color: #1e3a6e; flex-shrink: 0; width: 72px; }
        .info-val { color: #ef4444; line-height: 1.5; }
        .info-val.date { color: #2d4a7a; }

        /* 안내 카드 */
        .notice-card {
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px); background: rgba(239,246,255,.6);
            border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,.15); border-radius: 16px; padding: 18px 20px;
            font-size: 13px; color: #4a6fa5; line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .notice-card strong { color: #1e3a6e; font-weight: 700; }

        /* 버튼 */
        .btn-gray {
            display: block; width: 100%; padding: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6b7280, #4b5563); color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800;
            text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(107,114,128,.3); transition: all .15s;
        }
        .btn-gray:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(107,114,128,.4); }

        @media (max-width: 860px) { .hero-panel { display: none; } .content-panel { padding: 32px 20px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- 왼쪽 히어로 -->
<div class="hero-panel">
    <div class="logo">I<span class="hl">code</span>U</div>
    <div class="hero-icon">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ef4444"><path d="M13 13h-2V7h2v6Zm0 4h-2v-2h2v2ZM12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2Zm0 18c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8Z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">계정<br>이용 정지</h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">커뮤니티 운영정책 위반으로 인해 계정 이용이 일시적으로 제한되었습니다.</p>
</div>

<!-- 오른쪽 콘텐츠 -->
<div class="content-panel">
    <div class="content-inner">

        <div class="glass-card">
            <div class="card-label">정지 정보</div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">정지 사유</span>
                <span class="info-val">{{banReason}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">만료 일시</span>
                <span class="info-val date">{{expiredAt}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice-card">
            회원 상태 및 정지 관련 문의는 고객센터로 연락 바랍니다.<br>
            <strong>고객센터</strong> : 051-1234-1234
        </div>

        <a href="/logout" class="btn-gray">메인으로 돌아가기</a>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>